            "content_html": "<main>\n    <p>\n\tSummary of BCD changes from <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 9 February 2026\">Monday, 9 February 2026</time></a> through <time title=\"Monday, 16 February 2026\">Monday, 16 February 2026</time></strong><a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-02-16.html\" title=\"permalink\">🔗</a>\n    </p>\n    <hr>\n\n\n          <p class=\"callout\"><strong>7 new universal implementations</strong></p>\n          <section class=\"added implementations\">\n\t            <h4>CSS</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ text-indent ➞ each-line\n                      \t<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text/#valdef-text-indent-each-line\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Chrome</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ text-indent ➞ hanging\n                      \t<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text/#valdef-text-indent-hanging\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Chrome</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Values/basic-shape/shape\">css ➞ types ➞ basic-shape ➞ shape</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n\t            <h4>HTTP</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/HTTP/Reference/Headers/Accept-Encoding#zstd\">http ➞ headers ➞ Accept-Encoding ➞ zstd</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n\n          \n\n                      <span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/HTTP/Reference/Headers/Content-Encoding#zstd\">http ➞ headers ➞ Content-Encoding ➞ zstd</a>\n                      </span>\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n\t            <h4>WEBASSEMBLY</h4>\n              <ol>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>webassembly ➞ api ➞ Memory ➞ toFixedLengthBuffer\n                      \t<a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#dom-memory-tofixedlengthbuffer\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n                  <li>\n                      <span>webassembly ➞ api ➞ Memory ➞ toResizableBuffer\n                      \t<a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#dom-memory-toresizablebuffer\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg\" alt=\"Spec link\"></a>\n                      </span>\n\n          \n\n                    \n                    <b><br></b> \n                    <span class=\"browsers\">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> \n                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>\n                    <span class=\"ni3 engines\"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>\n\n                  </li>\n              </ol>\n          </section>\n\n  <hr>\n  <ul id=\"prev-next\">\n  \t<li>Previous report: <a href=\"\"><time title=\"Monday, 9 February 2026\">Monday, 9 February 2026</time></a></li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <footer>\n  \t<p>\n  \t<a href=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/\">BCD Watch</a>: A service of <a href=\"https://igalia.com\"><img src=\"https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/igalia-logo.png\" alt=\"Igalia\"></a>\n  \t</p>\n  \t<p>\n  \tSubscribe: <a href=\"feed.rss\">RSS</a> • <a href=\"feed.atom\">Atom</a> • <a href=\"feed.json\">JSON</a>\n  \t</p>\n\t\t<div class=\"subfooter\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"details\">\n\t\t\tThis report was generated by diffing <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v7.3.1\">v7.3.1</a> <small>(Friday, 6 February 2026)</small> and <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data/releases/tag/v7.3.2\">v7.3.2</a> <small>(Friday, 13 February 2026)</small>\n\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t</div>\n  </footer>\n  </main>",
